### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/v1
@apiKey = k49_DemoKey49DevLocalTest0000

### ===========================
### FACTURA ELECTRÓNICA
### ===========================

### Crear factura
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "establishment": "001",
  "issue_point": "001",
  "sequence_number": "000000042",
  "issue_date": "2026-04-04",
  "recipient": {
    "id_type": "04",
    "id": "1790012345001",
    "name": "Empresa Cliente S.A.",
    "address": "Av. Principal 123, Quito",
    "email": "contabilidad@cliente.com",
    "phone": "0991234567"
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "main_code": "SRV-001",
      "description": "Servicio de hosting mensual - Plan Business",
      "unit_of_measure": "UNIDAD",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unit_price": 50.00,
      "discount": 0.00,
      "taxes": [
        {
          "code": "2",
          "rate_code": "4",
          "rate": 15.00
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "main_code": "SRV-002",
      "description": "Dominio .ec renovación anual",
      "unit_of_measure": "UNIDAD",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unit_price": 35.00,
      "discount": 5.00,
      "taxes": [
        {
          "code": "2",
          "rate_code": "4",
          "rate": 15.00
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "payments": [
    {
      "payment_method": "20",
      "total": 84.25,
      "term": 0,
      "time_unit": "days"
    }
  ],
  "additional_info": {
    "Dirección": "Av. Principal 123, Quito",
    "Email": "contabilidad@cliente.com",
    "Observación": "Servicios del mes de abril 2026"
  }
}

### Consultar factura por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/d290f1ee-6c54-4b01-90e6-d701748f0851
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Listar facturas
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices?status=AUTHORIZED&date_from=2026-04-01&date_to=2026-04-30&page=1&per_page=20
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Descargar XML autorizado
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/d290f1ee-6c54-4b01-90e6-d701748f0851/xml
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Descargar RIDE (PDF)
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/d290f1ee-6c54-4b01-90e6-d701748f0851/ride
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Reenviar email
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoices/d290f1ee-6c54-4b01-90e6-d701748f0851/resend-email
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### ===========================
### CONSULTA SRI DIRECTA
### ===========================

### Consultar autorización por clave de acceso
GET {{baseUrl}}/sri/authorize/0404202601179001234500110010010000000421234567817
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### ===========================
### TENANT
### ===========================

### Obtener perfil del tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Verificar estado del certificado
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/certificate/status
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Subir certificado .p12
# POST {{baseUrl}}/tenant/certificate
# Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary
# (usar Postman o curl para multipart)

### ===========================
### PUNTOS DE EMISIÓN
### ===========================

### Listar puntos de emisión
GET {{baseUrl}}/emission-points
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Crear punto de emisión
POST {{baseUrl}}/emission-points
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "establecimiento": "002",
  "punto_emision": "001",
  "direccion": "Sucursal Norte, Av. América N32-123, Quito"
}

### Consultar secuenciales
GET {{baseUrl}}/emission-points/e290f1ee-6c54-4b01-90e6-d701748f0852/sequentials
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### ===========================
### MÉTRICAS
### ===========================

### Resumen de actividad
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### ===========================
### HEALTH
### ===========================

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/q/health

### Readiness
GET http://localhost:8080/q/health/ready

### Liveness
GET http://localhost:8080/q/health/live
